@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vlktiw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((0.32 / (v2 + 0.48 / v2 + 0.14)) * (wp.sin(v2 + 0.94) - wp.cos(v1 + 0.39)))
    tmp = tmp
    v0 = wp.cos(0.29)
    v2 = v1
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.exp((tmp + 0.13 * tmp + 0.27)))
    data[tid] = v0
